snippet.title: Tactical Combat Department [PC] Trailer
snippet.description:
Tactical Combat Department is a tactical turn-based strategy game inspired by SWAT games, where you command a special intervention squad that intervenes in various situations and environments.

More details here: https://worthplaying.com/game/15736-tactical-combat-department/

Tactical Combat Department will have a playable demo during Steam Next Fest (October 1 to 7), followed by Steam Early Access on October 14, 2021.

Tactical Combat Department is coming to PC (Steam) in 2022.
